  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/619470/extras/c888e761a6b799378f722ffa2f1ca3ab.avif?t=1596614667\" width=616 height=102 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/619470/extras/19d0f5035d17e6ac380b122f29ec64ef.poster.avif?t=1596614667\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/619470/extras/19d0f5035d17e6ac380b122f29ec64ef.webm?t=1596614667\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/619470/extras/19d0f5035d17e6ac380b122f29ec64ef.mp4?t=1596614667\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Boss Defiance - Heroic Edition is an arcade/action competitive and asymmetric game with both multiplayer and local co-op up to 4 players.<br><br>You can choose to be a powerful Boss or one of the brave Heroes fighting him.<br>Boss will fight 'till death, a dungeon after the other, facing the other players/characters in supercool dungeon battle arenas.<br>To succeed, it needs to reach the end of the dungeon, slaying all the Heroes in will find in his way.<br>Heroes, instead, need to cooperate in order to stop their evil enemy from arriving at the end of the arena, winning.<br>The game features two different modes: Normal Mode and Beast Mode, where the Boss is even more powerful and dangerous!<br>Both modes can be played up to 4 players.<br><br>Rediscover the pleasure of playing side by side with your friends in this exciting action couch game, and spend countless hours of fun !<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/619470/extras/006896722ce3c817920ec9fe4d1da3fe.avif?t=1596614667\" width=616 height=102 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/619470/extras/80818beea190b0ce0f507f643a5478dd.poster.avif?t=1596614667\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/619470/extras/80818beea190b0ce0f507f643a5478dd.webm?t=1596614667\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/619470/extras/80818beea190b0ce0f507f643a5478dd.mp4?t=1596614667\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/619470/extras/72860f5af4a67b4b1d3362f58e3c5f0b.webp?t=1596614667\" width=24 height=24 /></span> 8 different Heroes you can play (2 new amazing heroes, the Pyromancer and the Alchemist!)<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/619470/extras/72860f5af4a67b4b1d3362f58e3c5f0b.webp?t=1596614667\" width=24 height=24 /></span> 3 different Bosses (you can play them too!)<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/619470/extras/72860f5af4a67b4b1d3362f58e3c5f0b.webp?t=1596614667\" width=24 height=24 /></span> amazing retro-inspired pixel art<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/619470/extras/72860f5af4a67b4b1d3362f58e3c5f0b.webp?t=1596614667\" width=24 height=24 /></span> tons of fixes and updates<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/619470/extras/72860f5af4a67b4b1d3362f58e3c5f0b.webp?t=1596614667\" width=24 height=24 /></span> revamped design<br><br>Everyone who purchased the original Boss Defiance will get the Heroic Edition for free and will be able to download a brand new 28 pages Concept Book featuring all the studies, sketches and tests made during the development by the team.<br><br>You can't miss it!",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/619470/extras/c888e761a6b799378f722ffa2f1ca3ab.avif?t=1596614667\" width=616 height=102 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/619470/extras/19d0f5035d17e6ac380b122f29ec64ef.poster.avif?t=1596614667\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/619470/extras/19d0f5035d17e6ac380b122f29ec64ef.webm?t=1596614667\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/619470/extras/19d0f5035d17e6ac380b122f29ec64ef.mp4?t=1596614667\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Boss Defiance - Heroic Edition is an arcade/action competitive and asymmetric game with both multiplayer and local co-op up to 4 players.<br><br>You can choose to be a powerful Boss or one of the brave Heroes fighting him.<br>Boss will fight 'till death, a dungeon after the other, facing the other players/characters in supercool dungeon battle arenas.<br>To succeed, it needs to reach the end of the dungeon, slaying all the Heroes in will find in his way.<br>Heroes, instead, need to cooperate in order to stop their evil enemy from arriving at the end of the arena, winning.<br>The game features two different modes: Normal Mode and Beast Mode, where the Boss is even more powerful and dangerous!<br>Both modes can be played up to 4 players.<br><br>Rediscover the pleasure of playing side by side with your friends in this exciting action couch game, and spend countless hours of fun !<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/619470/extras/006896722ce3c817920ec9fe4d1da3fe.avif?t=1596614667\" width=616 height=102 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/619470/extras/80818beea190b0ce0f507f643a5478dd.poster.avif?t=1596614667\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/619470/extras/80818beea190b0ce0f507f643a5478dd.webm?t=1596614667\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/619470/extras/80818beea190b0ce0f507f643a5478dd.mp4?t=1596614667\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/619470/extras/72860f5af4a67b4b1d3362f58e3c5f0b.webp?t=1596614667\" width=24 height=24 /></span> 8 different Heroes you can play (2 new amazing heroes, the Pyromancer and the Alchemist!)<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/619470/extras/72860f5af4a67b4b1d3362f58e3c5f0b.webp?t=1596614667\" width=24 height=24 /></span> 3 different Bosses (you can play them too!)<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/619470/extras/72860f5af4a67b4b1d3362f58e3c5f0b.webp?t=1596614667\" width=24 height=24 /></span> amazing retro-inspired pixel art<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/619470/extras/72860f5af4a67b4b1d3362f58e3c5f0b.webp?t=1596614667\" width=24 height=24 /></span> tons of fixes and updates<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/619470/extras/72860f5af4a67b4b1d3362f58e3c5f0b.webp?t=1596614667\" width=24 height=24 /></span> revamped design<br><br>Everyone who purchased the original Boss Defiance will get the Heroic Edition for free and will be able to download a brand new 28 pages Concept Book featuring all the studies, sketches and tests made during the development by the team.<br><br>You can't miss it!",
